@AzDeRi
I see you have a few servers built in onto this game, can i get whitelisted?

@qiip99

You must have java installed and classpath configured correctly. You can check it out by typing "java" in command prompt and hitting enter. If it says "is not recognized as an command" reinstall newest JRE.

After this running another of .bat files inside server folder should do the trick.
